data.description: Location! location! Don't miss the opportunity to live in a gated community, centrally located in Kissimmee. This single-family home features 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  First impression is the immaculate open tiled foyer, followed by the living room and dining room. Entertain and cook in this large kitchen with granite counters, island, microwave, range and refrigerator, next to a breakfast nook and a family room with a view to the open backyard with NO rear neighbors.   The laundry room includes washer and dryer.   Added features to this amazing beauty are a water softener, tinted windows, ceiling fans, screened in patio with a creek view that's connected to lake Tohopekaliga and a paved bike and walking trail next to the property.
